Custom Crates in Las Vegas — Built to Protect, Engineered to Perform

Every shipment, every product, and every logistics challenge is different — which means standard packaging solutions just don’t cut it. Whether you’re shipping fragile equipment, oversized machinery, trade show materials, or high-value goods, protection and precision matter. That’s where custom crates from Crates of Las Vegas make all the difference.

At Crates of Las Vegas, we specialize in crafting premium custom crates that are tailored to your exact specifications — engineered for unparalleled strength, optimized for your product, and designed to deliver peace of mind every time you ship.

If your business depends on secure, reliable transport — locally, nationally, or internationally — custom crates give you the protection and performance no off-the-shelf solution can match.

Why Choose Custom Crates?

Off-the-shelf boxes and generic packaging solutions may be quick, but they’re not built to handle the stresses of real-world transport — especially when heavy, delicate, or awkwardly shaped items are involved.

Custom crates give you:

✔ Perfect Fit — built to the exact dimensions and specifications of your cargo

✔ Superior Protection — engineered strength to protect against shock, vibration, and rough handling

✔ Material Optimization — wood, metal, sealed panels, rail-ready designs, and more

✔ Compliance Ready — built to meet industry and international standards

✔ Cost-Efficient Shipping — better utilization of space and reduced freight damage

When you invest in a custom crate, you’re not just buying packaging — you’re investing in a stronger logistics strategy.

Tailored Crate Solutions for Every Need

No two shipments are the same — and our custom crates are built to reflect that. Whether you need one custom crate or a series of specialized builds, Crates of Las Vegas has the expertise and production capacity to deliver.

Our custom crate services include:

Precision Engineered Crates
Designed for specific load profiles and handling conditions, with structural reinforcement where it matters most.

Heavy-Duty Industrial Crates
Perfect for machinery, automotive parts, electronics housings, and other oversized or weighty cargo.

Fragile and Sensitivity-Focused Crates
Designed with internal padding, braces, and support systems to protect delicate or high-value items.

Export-Ready Crates
Built for global shipping with engineered strength and compatibility for air, sea, or ground transport.

Custom Skids & Pallet Crates
Built to standard or precise dimensions with integrated skid bases for forklift handling and logistics efficiency.

Every crate we build is manufactured with care, precision, and priority on performance — ensuring your cargo arrives in the same condition it left.

Built for Strength, Designed for Your Product

The core advantage of custom crates lies in how they’re engineered. At Crates of Las Vegas, we don’t guess — we design.

High-grade material selection:
We use premium structural lumber and reinforced components that support weight, absorb shock, and resist environmental stresses.

Structural optimization:
Every panel, corner, and threshold is planned to support your cargo specifically — not generically.

Internal support systems:
For delicate or sensitive goods, we can incorporate bracing, blocking, padding, and partitioning systems that enhance protection and prevent movement during transit.

Clinical precision:
From dimensions to load-bearing calculations, every custom crate we build meets engineering requirements that prioritize safety and durability.

